=== The Vortex ===
* 1. Choice, ''''Proceed further'''', {{icon|astral rift difficulty easy}} 2 or ''''Expose sample to flame'''', {{icon|astral rift difficulty hard}} 6. Gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}.
* 2a. Proceed further, narrative, Gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}.
* 2b. Expose sample to flame, narrative, gives {{iconify|Engineering}} Research and the Vortex Fuel modifier, granting +10% {{iconify|Energy}} for 10 years.
* 2c. Expose sample to flame (Failure outcome), your scientist dies, gives {{iconify|Exotic gases}} and {{reward|ast|ast3|empty|empty}}, the rift ends.
* 3. Narrative, gives {{iconify|Physics}} Research and {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}.
* 4. Choice, ''''Flash lights'''', {{icon|astral rift difficulty hard}} 6 or ''''Observe'''' {{icon|astral rift difficulty easy}} 2. Gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}.
* 5a. Narrative, gives {{reward|ast|ast2|empty|empty}}.
* 5b. Narrative, gives {{iconify|Physics}} Research.
* 6. Narrative, gives the Ever Spinning Top Relic.
